{"tid":2428784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲臘親王周一轉院治療感染 皇儲查理斯日前到醫院討論皇室未來角色","createTime":"2021-03-01T20:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T23:19:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3fc21bf4f14f58f9384aabc8676bb5d1befe16","tid":2428784,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T20:46:31.000Z","msg":"英國皇夫菲臘親王入院已近兩星期，健康狀況令人關注。英媒引述白金漢宮聲明指，菲臘親王因感染而入院，目前治療正產生作用，但預計未來幾日仍未能出院。至於皇儲查理斯日前涉嫌違反封城防疫措施，到醫院探望老父，據報是菲臘親王希望跟他討論皇室未來角色。白金漢宮周一發聲明指，菲臘親王周一由倫敦英皇愛德華七世醫院轉往聖巴塞洛繆醫院 (St Bartholomew&rsquo;s Hospital)。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210301/APUZIZRGWFDJZFE2JYFTIATZXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210301%2FAPUZIZRGWFDJZFE2JYFTIATZXU%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt18yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=1439ed5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210301%2FAPUZIZRGWFDJZFE2JYFTIATZXU%2F&h=f2c359cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210301/APUZIZRGWFDJZFE2JYFTIATZXU/</a>"},{"pid":"65523787e91d5055a0caab34468db231eceee021","tid":2428784,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T20:55:32.000Z","msg":"菲臘親王 1921年6月10日-（99歲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27968398b051e78a3894e7e52de1661311a60d80","tid":2428784,"uid":390761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T23:19:16.000Z","msg":"成日覺得查理斯等到死個日<br />\n<br />\n都冇得做英國皇帝"}]}